OL,4,G0245FKlimt & The Kiss
OL,5,     GExperts examine 'The Kiss' -
OL,6,     GGustav Klimt's iconic painting
OL,7,     Gfrom the early 20th century - and
OL,8,     Gestablish just what makes it such
OL,9,     Gan enduring, endearing piece.
OL,10,G0400FLandmark
OL,11,     GArtists and communities team up
OL,12,     Gfor a chance to create the UK's
OL,13,     Gnext major landmark, hosted by
OL,14,     GGemma Cairney.
OL,15,G0500FAuction
OL,16,     GStep inside the great auction
OL,17,     Ghouses of the world and discover
OL,18,     Gthe bidding frenzies within. In
OL,19,     Gthis opening episode, Sotheby's
OL,20,     Gsells The Lock by John Constable.
